				I'm not on a PvP server, however, I will mention that hiding, sneaking and invis are good, as long as your opponent doesn't have see invisible. I was duelling a Rogue the other day who ended up on a long run back to his corpse, because he thought I couldn't see him as he snuck around to backstab me.<BR>
If you are a caster, and you have see invis, it could be a good defense tactic to give yourself see invis as well since anyone with invis or sneak could approach you quitely when they're about to attack.
